            "title": "Introduction",
            "id": 86509,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Las funciones necesitan <strong>múltiples parámetros</strong> para realizar tareas con más piezas de datos, como el nombre y apellido de un nuevo jugador.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 350px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF&#xA;   }&#xA;   button {&#xA;    width: 200px;&#xA;    height: 30px;&#xA;    font-size: 20px;&#xA;    border-radius: 5px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    display: block;&#xA;    color: black;&#xA;    outline: none;&#xA;   }&#xA;   input {&#xA;    border-radius: 5px;&#xA;    padding: 10px;&#xA;    margin: 10px;&#xA;    outline: none;&#xA;   }&#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body id=&quot;main&quot;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h1&gt;Add Team Players&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&quot;Signup&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;div class=&quot;playerInput&quot;&gt; &#xA;    &lt;input id=&quot;firstNameInput&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; placeholder=&quot;First Name&quot;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;input id=&quot;surnameInput&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; placeholder=&quot;Last Name&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt; &#xA;   &lt;button onClick=&quot;add()&quot;&gt;Submit&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;   &lt;h3&gt;Current Team&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul id=playerList&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;full&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;script&gt;&#xA;   let number = 0;&#xA;   function add() {&#xA;    if (number &gt;= 3) {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;full&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;Team Full&quot;;&#xA;    } else {&#xA;     const firstName = document.getElementById(&quot;firstNameInput&quot;).value;&#xA;     const surname = document.getElementById(&quot;surnameInput&quot;).value;&#xA;     const node = document.createElement(&quot;P&quot;);&#xA;     const textnode = document.createTextNode(&quot;Added: &quot; + firstName +&#xA;      &quot; &quot; + surname);&#xA;     node.appendChild(textnode);&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;playerList&quot;).appendChild(node);&#xA;     number++;&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;firstNameInput&quot;).value = &quot;&quot;;&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;surnameInput&quot;).value = &quot;&quot;;&#xA;    }&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Previously",
            "id": 86514,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos crear funciones con un solo parámetro como <code>display(first_name)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(first_name)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(first_name)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"display(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alex&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"11\" /><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Alex\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>display</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y luego <code>first_name</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Comma",
            "id": 86511,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para agregar más parámetros a una función, codificamos una <strong>coma</strong> seguida del nombre del siguiente parámetro, como <code>last</code> para el apellido.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(first, last)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(first + \" /><text value=\"&quot; &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + last)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"display(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alex&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Morgan&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"23\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Alex Morgan\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>,</code> seguido de <code>last</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
